data.description: Move in condition property is vacant and can close quickly. Highly functional floor plan with main floor bedroom and 4 upper bedrooms. Updated kitchen will granite counters and newer appliances. Roof approximately 5 years old. Both full baths have been completely updated with new toilets, tubs, new vanity, new fixtures, tile floors, custom tile backsplash in showers. Half bath has newer vanity and fixtures. Main interior level recently painted. Fantastic community amenities include bike and walking trails, four rec centers (included in HOA fees), schools, shops, mall, light rail and easy access to E-470 and I25.
